<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:200px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4128-j/Terrified" style="width:200px;" alt="Terrified" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:200px;">
<p>信息6</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>研究员Gwent：</strong>别再往伤口上撒盐了，求你了。</p>
<p><em>研究员Gwent执行程序A。结果：信息7。</em></p>
